{"tid":2069071,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"搞個玩具同樂日都想拎區議會16m咁撚大貪，六千五比多你啦","createTime":"2020-06-18T06:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T11:38:02.000Z","uid":7439,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"32d050209fde074195eedc3a36a8a5faf62940d6","tid":2069071,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"沙田區議會<br />\n文化、體育及社區發展委員會<br />\n<br />\n二零二零/二一年度撥款申請<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/st/doc/2020_2023/tc/committee_meetings_doc/CSCDC/18936/st_cscdc_2020_032_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fst%2Fdoc%2F2020_2023%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2FCSCDC%2F18936%2Fst_cscdc_2020_032_tc.pdf&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=85ffa7d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/st/doc/2020_2023/tc/committee_meetings_doc/CSCDC/18936/st_cscdc_2020_032_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<blockquote>申請金額($) 工作小組建議撥款額($)<br />\n新界東青年體育會 沙田區籃球同樂日 <span style=\"color: blue;\">164,800.00</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">6,500.00</span><br />\n新界東青年體育會 挑戰無極限 164,800.00 0.00<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新界東青年體育會 精采人生展活力 164,800.00 0.00<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/83077035_814987808984234_6022936293921521664_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=e007fa&amp;_nc_ohc=tdcB_AtpCh4AX-L8v2H&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=9da34a57f2711ccb6dcba9bd2072fab6&amp;oe=5F114B07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F83077035_814987808984234_6022936293921521664_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3De007fa%26_nc_ohc%3DtdcB_AtpCh4AX-L8v2H%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D9da34a57f2711ccb6dcba9bd2072fab6%26oe%3D5F114B07&h=da6b2abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https